body:
**功能**

1. 附魔台添加分解魔咒(可选;
2. 铁砧添加转移魔咒(全);
3. 解除铁砧过于昂贵;
4. 物品化村民(空手按 [alt]);
5. 物品最大叠加 [16] 的物品提升为[64];
6. 击杀敌对生物有几率掉落生物蛋(可配置;
7. 添加一些配方如: 刷怪笼、鞘翅;
8. 添加时间、FPS HUB(可配置;
9. 添加物品经验书、升级卷轴;
_配置文件:STConfig.properties_

**Description**

1. Added decomposition spells (optional) to Enchant Table;
2. Anvil added Transfer Spell (full);
3. Lifting the anvil is too expensive;
4. Materialized villagers (empty hand press [alt]);
5. Item with maximum stack [16] increased to [64];
6. Kill enemy pairs have a chance to drop creature eggs (configurable;
7. Add some recipes such as: brush monster cage, elytra;
8. Added time, FPS HUB(configurable;
9. Add item experience book, upgrade scroll;
_configuration file: STConfig.properties_
